I have Editor Extensions installed and a bunch of other mods as well. THe thing is X and C shorcuts for symetry mode are not working suddenly. I allways worked and now they don't. Please help!
LOG: http://www.filedropper.com/outputlog_4

this is my mod list: https://imgur.com/stREkum

Edited October 24, 2017 by Agustin

On mobile right now, but it sounds like you downloaded the wrong person of the mod. This is the only mod that has a very specific requirement of a compiled version for each version of KSP.

What version of KSP are you running and what version of The Mod do you have installed?

Ok I solved it. I don't know what caused it, but I went to the settings in the main manu and relocated the keybings that were somehow lost. It all works now.
